                           Niklas Purger, der Comthur und Ulrich Hirssauer, Stadtschreiber. </p></seal></sealDesc></physDesc></msDesc></sourceDesc></fileDesc><encodingDesc><projectDesc default="false"><p><label type="contentual-editing">Dissertation Korbinian Grünwald</label></p></projectDesc></encodingDesc><profileDesc><creation>
            <placeName>Wien</placeName>
            <date when="14530705">1453 VII 05</date>
            <origDate instant="false">zu Wienn, an phincztag nach sant Ulreichs tag.</origDate></creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><facsimile><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Urkunden_03524_r.jpg"/></surface><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Urkunden_03524_v.jpg"/></surface></facsimile><text><body><div type="abstract" resp="kg"><p>
               <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3524"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__simon_poetel_QGW_II_II_2412">Simon Potl, des
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">rats</roleName> der stat und
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_stephan">kirchmaister</roleName> sant Steffans kirchen zu Wienn <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__johann_zwettler_QGW_II_II_3524"><add>geschefftleut</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_purger_QGW_II_III_3758">Niclas Purger, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">burger</roleName> daselbs <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__johann_zwettler_QGW_II_II_3524"><add>geschefftleut</add></roleName></rs>, und <rs type="person" ref="pe__barbara_QGW_II_II_3524">Barbara, jecz Hannsen Malchinger <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__johann_malchinger_QGW_II_II_3524">hausfrau</roleName>, die <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_zwettler_QGW_II_II_3524">emaln Hannsen Zwetler am
                           Salzgriezz, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">burger</roleName> zu Wienn <roleName type="dead">seligen</roleName></rs>, auch <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__johann_zwettler_QGW_II_II_3524">elichen</roleName> hat
                        gehabt, desselben Zwetler <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__johann_zwettler_QGW_II_II_3524">geschefftleut</roleName></rs>,</rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">beurkunden</triggerstring>, dass <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3524_men_1"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_zwettler_QGW_II_II_3524">dieser</rs></rs>
                     <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_haberpeunt_vor_karntnertor_1"><roleName type="owner" corresp="pe__johann_zwettler_QGW_II_II_3524">seinen</roleName>
                           Weingarten, <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-haberpeunt_vor_karntnertor">in der
                              Haberpeunt</roleName>
                           <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-buergerspital">gegen dem Spital
                              über gelegen</roleName>, des anderthalb hofstat ist, <roleName type="topo" corresp="pl__wien-immo_haberpeunt_vor_karntnertor_2">zenagst</roleName>
                           <rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_haberpeunt_vor_karntnertor_2"><roleName type="owner" corresp="pe__simon_ekker_QGW_II_II_3524"><rs type="person" ref="pe__simon_ekker_QGW_II_II_3524">Simons
                                    des Egker</rs></roleName> weingarten</rs>, <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3524_men_1"><rs type="fn" role="issuer">von <rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_haberpeunt_vor_karntnertor_1">dem</rs>
                                 man</rs>
                              <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="org" ref="org__wien-st_johann_in_der_kaerntnerstrasse">dem haus zu
                                    sand Johanns in der Kernerstrass hie zu Wienn</rs></rs>
                              <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><measure>½ lb dn.</measure>
                                 <triggerstring n="fn">zu Grunddienst</triggerstring></rs>
                              <triggerstring n="disp"><add>zu Grunddienst</add>
                           dient</triggerstring></rs></rs>,</rs> zu ainer ewigen <triggerstring n="disp">messe</triggerstring>, zwir in der wochen zu sprechen oder was das gut
                     getragen mag, <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="org" ref="org__wien-st_stephan-altar_st_georg"/></rs>
                     <triggerstring n="disp">geschafft</triggerstring> und die Messe während seiner
                     Krankheit <rs type="fn" role="other"><rs type="person" ref="pe__wolfgang_von_zwettl_QGW_II_II_3524"><roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_stephan-altar_st_georg-messe_zwettler_johann"><add>Kaplan</add></roleName>
                           <roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Wolfgangen von Zwetl</rs>
                        <triggerstring n="disp">verliehen habe</triggerstring></rs>.</rs> Sie <triggerstring n="disp">widmen nunmehr</triggerstring>
                  <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">mit Handen</triggerstring>
                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__andreas_giger_QGW_II_II_3246"><roleName type="title">pruder</roleName> Andres Giger, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_johann_in_der_kaerntnerstrasse">comenteur</roleName> des vorgenanten hauss zu sand Johanns</rs>,</rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><rs type="place" ref="pl__wien-immo_haberpeunt_vor_karntnertor_1">den Weingarten</rs></rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="recipient">zu <rs type="org" ref="org__wien-st_stephan-altar_st_georg-messe_zwettler_johann">der auf sand
                        Jorgen altar in sant Steffans kirchen gestifteten Messe</rs></rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">und übertragen die Lehenschaft</triggerstring>
                  <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">die Lehenschaft</triggerstring>
                     <rs type="org" ref="org__wien">an Bürgermeister und Rath</rs></rs>.</rs>
            </p></div><div type="seal"><p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3524"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Siegler: <rs type="person" ref="pe__simon_poetel_QGW_II_II_2412">Simon Pötl</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_purger_QGW_II_III_3758">Niklas Purger</rs>,
                        <rs type="person" ref="pe__andreas_giger_QGW_II_II_3246">der Comthur</rs>
                     und <rs type="person" ref="pe__ulrich_hirssauer_QGW_II_II_3239">Ulrich
                        Hirssauer, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien">Stadtschreiber</roleName></rs>.</rs></rs>
            </p></div><div type="lists"><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/placeList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/personList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/eventList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/orgList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/></div></body></text></TEI>